Ext.data.JsonP['TableView']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>TableView</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-41845779\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>TableView</h1>\n    <p>Demonstrates basic use of TableView control.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox admonition admonition-info aui-message hint shadowed information-macro has-no-icon\">\n            <div class=\"title\">App Folder Location</div>\n            <p>alloy/test/apps/<strong class=\" \">ui/tableview</strong>    </p>\n    </div>\n        <p>    <span style=\"color: #484848;\">\nA <a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TableView\">TableView</a> is used to present vertically scrolling rows of information, optionally organized into sections. A TableView can include a SearchBar to let users search the table contents.<br>    </br></span>\n    </p>\n    <p>    <img src=\"images/download/attachments/41845779/screenshot.png\" alt=\"images/download/attachments/41845779/screenshot.png\" class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" width=\"500\">\n        </img></p>\n    <p>The main index.xml view displays two TableView controls in separate tabs. The second tab uses sections to organize table rows    </p>\n    <p>To create a table, you add a &lt;TableView/&gt; element that contains one or more &lt;TableViewRow&gt; elements, and optionally &lt;HeaderView/&gt; and &lt;FooterView/&gt; elements. Use &lt;TableViewSection/&gt; elements to organize rows into sections. To include a search bar in the table, include a &lt;SearchBar/&gt; element; to specify the field to search on, add a <tt class=\" \">filterAttribute</tt> attribute to the &lt;TableView/&gt; element, as shown below.    </p>\n    <div class=\"confbox programlisting defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\">\n                    <div class=\"title\">app/views/index.xml</div>\n                <div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" class=\"defaultnew syntaxhighlighter scroll-html-formatted-code\" data-title=\"app/views/index.xml\">\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;TabGroup&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Tab title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Basic Rows&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">            &lt;Window title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Basic Rows&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                &lt;TableView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;HeaderView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;View backgroundColor=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;#a00&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> height=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;50dp&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;/HeaderView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;FooterView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;View backgroundColor=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;#0a0&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> height=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;50dp&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;/FooterView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;TableViewRow&gt;&lt;Label&gt;Row </code><code class=\"value\">1</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Label&gt;&lt;/TableViewRow&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;TableViewRow&gt;&lt;Label&gt;Row </code><code class=\"value\">2</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Label&gt;&lt;/TableViewRow&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;TableViewRow&gt;&lt;Label&gt;Row </code><code class=\"value\">3</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Label&gt;&lt;/TableViewRow&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;TableViewRow&gt;&lt;Label&gt;Row </code><code class=\"value\">4</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Label&gt;&lt;/TableViewRow&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;TableViewRow&gt;&lt;Label&gt;Row </code><code class=\"value\">5</code><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Label&gt;&lt;/TableViewRow&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                &lt;/TableView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">            &lt;/Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;/Tab&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;Tab title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Sections &amp;amp; Rows&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">            &lt;Window title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Sections &amp;amp; Rows&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                &lt;TableView filterAttribute=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;title&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;SearchBar platform=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;android,ios&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;TableViewSection&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;HeaderView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                            &lt;View backgroundColor=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;#a00&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> height=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;50dp&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;/HeaderView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;FooterView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                            &lt;View backgroundColor=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;#0a0&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\"> height=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;50dp&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;/FooterView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Row 1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Row 2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Row 3&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;/TableViewSection&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;TableViewSection headerTitle=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Section 2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Row 1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Row 2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Row 3&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;/TableViewSection&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;TableViewSection headerTitle=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Section 3&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Row 1&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Row 2&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                        &lt;TableViewRow title=</code><code class=\"string\">&quot;Row 3&quot;</code><code class=\"plain\">/&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                    &lt;/TableViewSection&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">                &lt;/TableView&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">            &lt;/Window&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">        &lt;/Tab&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">    &lt;/TabGroup&gt;</code></div>\n<div class=\"line\"><code class=\"plain\">&lt;/Alloy&gt;</code></div>\n</div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-41845779_TableView-SeeAlso\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>See Also</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>    <span style=\"color: #484848;\">\n<a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"#!/api/Titanium.UI.TableView\">Titanium.UI.TableView</a> API reference    </span>\n    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>    <span style=\"color: #484848;\">\n<a class=\"document-link unresolved\" href=\"#!/guide/TableView-section-src-41845779\">TableView Binding</a> sample application<br>    </br></span>\n    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=41845779\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"TableView"});